Event name: Kyy's sexy beard

Plot: Kyyyyyyyy has a very nice beard but one day wanted to wax it!
She was sad we made her have a beard! :(

Kyy approaches different players asking help with her humiliating dilemma. On the side she also offers a reward for the capture of one Laros the butt, dwarf of renowned evil powers who has cursed her with this horrid face fuzz.

Taz grabs kyys beard and trims it ;)

Laros, on the top of the windowless tower, keeps chanting dancing over his campfire burning even stronger pieces of maulber fur on his Kyy doll.

Suddenly Laros trips on a stone and falls into the campfire and burns his big bum!
